  Summary: The artifact is a class-bearing Spring Boot cache auto-configuration module. Its published runtime dependencies are only spring-boot and spring-context-support, but meaningful coverage of its central auto-configuration path requires Spring Boot's auto-configuration and test context runner support.
  
